{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/store_page_gif.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">shapez is a low-stakes factory building game all about the automation of shapes production. Extract basic shapes with miners, cut them into segments and combine them into brand-new, unique shapes. Stack multiple layers of different shapes on top of each other &amp; deliver them to the HUB to advance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_ADVANCE.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, new buildings are unlocked and the required shapes become more complex. Extract paint and use them to color your shapes. Spread out across the infinite sandbox to acquire different shapes and increase your production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_EXPAND.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leverage copy-paste tools to massively expand your factory as demand increases and shapes get more complex. Mix paint to create new colors, stack many layers of shapes and increase throughput as necessary. After all, it\u2019s not an idle game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get creative with optional wiring &amp; logic to optimize your factory to your liking and maybe even make a powerful machine that can make every shape possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_OPTIMIZE.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With no enemies, timers or resource limits to worry about, shapez is a game that allows you to take on factory building at your own pace while progressively tackling more complex levels, if you\u2019re looking for a challenge.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Painter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/5bfeacb11c3956d4a487c472c4a196d6117d8e17.jpg"},{"name":"Cutter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/1c484ff8a7b9e1d653f224bc80aae18d1ed186d4.jpg"},{"name":"Rotater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/a00e14dac175fc6b8105891551fdaa0cf7a266ec.jpg"},{"name":"Wait, they stack?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/7426e2c69bd8b1940d2092be1b976623d7f780a5.jpg"},{"name":"Now it's easy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/8926b70ac081f1242d88c3cf1523dff149f4f8be.jpg"},{"name":"Wires","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/f26f0a4a810c12e3660b76c624f103e0d29904b6.jpg"},{"name":"Storage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/be4b6647f6f385cc91bc117cffe35b79b3351fd8.jpg"},{"name":"Freedom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/9631bb674822a499ce64f8358133512f02e25bb6.jpg"},{"name":"Computer Guy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/4299c0edfbb6de70f7f472d99d9fb351fe9b6620.jpg"},{"name":"The logo!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1318690/c1d3293964648714e21df60a62e15682cdacd7ba.jpg"}],"total":45},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1318690?t=1734619281","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1318690?t=1734619281","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734619281","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734619281","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":1930750,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Try the shapez Demo!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give the game a go for free with the shapez Demo! Play through the game until level 7 to get a feel for the game before you unlock the full version. You can continue building your Demo factory!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/store_page_gif.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">shapez is a low-stakes factory building game all about the automation of shapes production. Extract basic shapes with miners, cut them into segments and combine them into brand-new, unique shapes. Stack multiple layers of different shapes on top of each other &amp; deliver them to the HUB to advance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_ADVANCE.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, new buildings are unlocked and the required shapes become more complex. Extract paint and use them to color your shapes. Spread out across the infinite sandbox to acquire different shapes and increase your production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_EXPAND.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leverage copy-paste tools to massively expand your factory as demand increases and shapes get more complex. Mix paint to create new colors, stack many layers of shapes and increase throughput as necessary. After all, it\u2019s not an idle game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get creative with optional wiring &amp; logic to optimize your factory to your liking and maybe even make a powerful machine that can make every shape possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/extras/shapez_1_store_banner_gif_OPTIMIZE.gif?t=1734619281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With no enemies, timers or resource limits to worry about, shapez is a game that allows you to take on factory building at your own pace while progressively tackling more complex levels, if you\u2019re looking for a challenge.</p>","developers":["Tobias Springer"],"dlc":[1625400,1573840],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318690/header.jpg?t=1734619281","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"shapez | shapez.io | Copyright 2020-2024 tobspr Games<br><strong>Privacy policy</strong>: ","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2 Ghz or faster<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2048 MB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Any<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 300 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Please report any issues in the discord!</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Re